{"article_id":"SXykdOrP98PRwFqT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Turkey has vowed to reveal all details about the killing of journalist Jamal Khashoggi ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"after Saudi Arabia admitted for the first time","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he had been killed in its consulate in Istanbul .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"`` Turkey will never allow a cover-up , ''","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"a ruling party spokesperson said .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Saudi Arabia suggested on Friday","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Mr Khashoggi ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"a prominent Saudi critic , had died in a `` fist fight '' .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Turkish officials previously said","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"he had been deliberately killed inside the consulate ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and his body dismembered .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Earlier this week , unnamed Turkish officials told media outlets","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"they had audio and visual evidence","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"to prove this .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"The Saudi kingdom has come under intense pressure","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"to explain Mr Khashoggi 's disappearance","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"after he entered the Istanbul consulate on 2 October","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to seek paperwork for his forthcoming marriage .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Until Friday , it had denied knowledge of his whereabouts","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and insisted","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"he had left the building alive .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Turkish police and prosecutors have been searching the consulate as well as the consul 's residence this week for evidence of what unfolded .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"On Friday they widened their search to a nearby forest ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"where unnamed officials believe","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"his body may have been disposed of .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"The kingdom says","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"a fight broke out between Mr Khashoggi ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"who had fallen out of favour with the Saudi government ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"and people","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"who met him in the consulate","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"- ending with his death .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"It says","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"investigations are under way ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"and so far 18 Saudi nationals have been arrested .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Unnamed officials","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"speaking to Reuters news agency and the New York Times","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"say","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"the Saudis did not know the whereabouts of the body","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"after it was handed to a `` local collaborator ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"to dispose of .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"In addition to the arrests , two senior officials have been sacked over the affair","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"- deputy intelligence chief Ahmad al-Assiri and Saud al-Qahtani , senior aide to Crown Prince Mohammed Bin Salman .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"The Saudi authorities have yet to give evidence","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"to support this version of events .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Observers are questioning","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"whether Saudi Arabia 's Western allies will find their account of a `` botched rendition '' convincing","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"and whether it will persuade them not to take punitive action against them .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"US President Donald Trump said","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"what had happened was `` unacceptable ''","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"but that the arrests were an important `` first step '' .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"The UK Foreign Office said","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"it was considering its next steps","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"after hearing the report .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` Turkey will reveal whatever had happened , ''","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"said Omer Celik of Turkey 's ruling AKP party ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"according to Anadolu news agency .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` Nobody should ever doubt about it .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"We are not accusing anyone in advance","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"but we do n't accept anything to remain covered [ up ] . ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Publicly Turkey has so far stopped short of blaming Saudi Arabia for the killing .","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"Turkish investigators , however , say","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"they have audio and video evidence","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"which shows","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Mr Khashoggi was killed by a team of Saudi agents inside the consulate","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and dismembered .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Reports in Turkish media this week gave gruesome details of what are said to be his final minutes .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Turkish media said","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"earlier this week","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"they had identified a 15-member team of suspected Saudi agents","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"who flew into and out of Istanbul on the day of the disappearance .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan spoke to Saudi King Salman on Friday evening ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"and the two agreed to continue co-operating in the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"The Saudi leadership will now be hoping","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that its belated admission","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that Khashoggi did die , after all , inside its consulate","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"- coupled with a handful of sackings and arrests -","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"will be enough","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"to draw a line under this affair .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"It will not .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"This is only a first step","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"towards publicising the truth of what really happened .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Given the days of indignant denials by the Saudi leadership","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"it 's doubtful we would have even got this far","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"without sustained international pressure .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"There can only be one of two possible alternatives here :","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"either","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"- as many suspect -","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"the powerful Crown Prince Mohammed Bin Salman was to blame","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"or he had lost control of his inner circle ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"something most observers find hard to believe .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"MBS ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"as he is known ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"has a huge following amongst young patriotic Saudis","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"who see him as a visionary reformer .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"If that support were now to ebb away","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"then the crown prince could find himself dangerously isolated at court .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"German Chancellor Angela Merkel has condemned the killing `` in the strongest terms '' ,","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"calling the explanations","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"given of the circumstances of Mr Khashoggi 's death","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"`` inadequate '' .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"The UK Foreign Office described it as `` a terrible act ''","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"and said","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"the people behind the killing `` must be held to account '' .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"President Trump praised the kingdom","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"for acting quickly","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"the official explanation was `` credible '' ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"despite many US lawmakers expressing disbelief over the Saudi account .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Mr Trump stressed the importance of Saudi Arabia as a counterbalance to Iran in the Middle East ,","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"and pushed back against the need for sanctions against the country in light of the new information ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"talking about the effect of such a move on the US economy .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Earlier this week he warned of `` very severe '' consequences","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"if Saudi Arabia was proved to have killed the journalist .","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"A number of US lawmakers ,","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"including a Republican highly critical of the Saudis , Senator Lindsey Graham ,","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"they were sceptical about the report on the journalist 's death .","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"Australia announced","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"it is withdrawing from an investment summit in Saudi Arabia later this month","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"- joining a growing boycott","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"that includes the US , UK , Dutch and French finance ministers over the Khashoggi killing .","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte has called for a `` thorough investigation ''","depth":5},{"id":123,"text":"to make sure","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"`` all relevant facts will be clear as soon as possible '' .","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"Mr Khashoggi 's fiancée , Hatice Cengiz , questioned in a tweet what had happened to his body ,","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"saying :","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"`` The heart grieves ,","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"the eye tears ,","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"and with your separation we are saddened , my dear Jamal . ''","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"The Washington Post ,","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"for which Mr Khashoggi was a contributor ,","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"has released a previously unheard interview","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"he gave to Karen Attiah , the Global Opinions editor .","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"In it he said :","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"`` Our leaders see themselves as leaders","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"who know best ,","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"and people like me ... are just hindering the process for their reform . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":275,"left":234,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":151,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":142,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":140,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":0,"right":139,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":147,"right":149,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":144,"right":146,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":5,"right":143,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":143,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":8,"right":145,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":11,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":196,"right":232,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":196,"left":180,"right":195,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":180,"left":157,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":152,"right":153,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent